#

Lentil Soup with Spinach

40 min
$8.5
220 kcal
Difficulty: 25%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianHigh ProteinGluten-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

SoupHealthyComfort Food

Description

A hearty and nutritious lentil soup packed with spinach, offering comfort in every spoonful.

Ingredients

  • green lentils: 1 cup
  • fresh spinach: 2 cups
  • carrot: 1, diced
  • celery: 1 stalk, diced
  • onion: 1, diced
  • garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • vegetable broth or water: 4 cups
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • cumin: 1 teaspoon
  • bay leaf: 1
